A letter from Akira Kurosawa to Ingmar Bergman for his 70th birthday.
.
With 2024 beginning, don’t pressure yourself to make great art. It can come with experiences and wisdom and time.
.
From 2015-2017 I lived in Arizona not making a single piece of art and I still credit that period for the art I make now.
.
Sometimes it feels like I don’t make art. I just make the person the art comes from.
